# Data Deletion Request – PCSO Live Guide

We respect your privacy and your right to control your data.

Although **PCSO Live Guide** does not require account registration and does not directly store personal information such as names or emails, some limited data (such as device identifiers and purchase information) may be processed through third-party services like Google Play Billing and RevenueCat.

## Requesting Data Deletion

If you would like to request deletion of any data associated with your use of the app, you may contact us through the link below:


You can email us directly:

📧 taghoy2@gmail.com

## What Happens Next

* We will review your request within **3–5 business days**
* If applicable, we will coordinate with our service providers (e.g., RevenueCat, Google Play) to remove associated data
* You will receive confirmation once your request has been processed

## Notes

* Since we do not maintain user accounts, deletion requests may be limited to anonymized or device-related data
* Subscription and purchase records may be retained as required by Google Play policies and legal obligations

---

By using PCSO Live Guide, you acknowledge that you may request data deletion at any time through the methods above.
